#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&trojita; is an email program (\"client\") focused on IMAP email accounts, "
"where the mail remains on the server but is manipulated by the software you "
"run on the computer under your fingertips. It is designed to be simple (it "
"can be built using only one single dependent library), and fast and "
"efficient over the network, economizing resources and limiting data "
"transfer. Its GUI is intended to be uncluttered and efficient, and it "
"provides \"expensive mode\" data transfer, that reduces the length of its "
"conversation with the server to a minimum. It is a stand-alone program, not "
"part of a bigger or more complex suite. As it is under development, some "
"features are still missing."
msgstr ""
"&trojita; je email program (\"klijent\") fokusiran na IMAP račune e-pošte, "
"gdje mail ostaje na serveru, ali se manipulira od strane softvera pokrenutog "
"na računalu pod dohvatom ruke. Dizajniran je da bude jednostavan (može biti "
"izrađen koristeći samo jednu zavisnu biblioteku), i to brzo i efikasno preko "
"mreže, privređuje resurse i ograničava prijenos podataka. Njegov GUI je "
"trebao da bude pretrpan i efikasan, i pruža \"skupi mod\" transfer podataka, "
"koji smanjuje dužinu svoje komunikacije sa serverom na minimum. To je "
"samostalan program, a ne dio veće ili složenije građe. Kao što je u razvoju, "
"neke karakteristike još uvijek nedostaju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &trojita;"
msgstr "Koristeći &trojita;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&trojita; allows you to read, write, organize, search for, and send email. "
"If you've got an IMAP email account, &trojita; will allow you to access and "
"use it. IMAP is a protocol that allows your mail to stay on the server, "
"rather than downloading it to your local machine. However, &trojita; does in "
"fact download parts of your messages &ndash; even all of your messages "
"&ndash; for convenience. In the 1990s, most people used POP3 mailboxes, and "
"their email software downloaded all their messages, removing them from the "
"server. The disadvantage was that if you used any other computer, your "
"messages were not available. IMAP solves that problem by keeping the mail on "
"the server. The software you use on your local computer/cellphone simply "
"issues instructions (\"reply to this email,\" \"display this email,\" &etc;) "
"for the server to execute."
msgstr ""
"&trojita; vam omogućava da čitate, pišete, organizirate, tražite, i šaljete "
"email. Ako imate email IMAP račun, &trojita; će vam omogućiti pristup i "
"korišćenje. IMAP je protokol koji omogućava da vaš mail ostane na serveru, "
"umjesto preuzimanja na mašinu. Međutim,  &trojita; radi u stvari download "
"dijelovima vaše poruke &ndash; čak i sve vaše poruke &ndash; za praktičnost. "
"U 1990-ih, većina ljudi je koristila POP3 poštanske sandučiće, i njihove e-"
"mail softver je preuzimao sve njihove poruke, vadeći ih  iz servera. "
"Nedostatak je da ako ste koristili bilo koji drugi računar, vaše poruke nisu "
"bile dostupne. IMAP rješava taj problem tako što čuva email na serveru. "
"Softver koji koristite na vašem lokalnom računaru/mobitelu jednostavno "
"izdaje upute (\"odgovori na e-mail\", \"prikaži ovaj e-mail,\" i &etc;) za "
"server da izvrši."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First you need an IMAP account. There are many providers; <ulink url="
"\"http://fastmail.fm\">FastMail</ulink> is one; <ulink url=\"http://tuffmail."
"com\">Tuffmail</ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://pobox.com\">Pobox</ulink> are "
"others. Google's Gmail service provides IMAP access to your Gmail account "
"(Outlook and others do not). And if the manager of your &Microsoft; "
"<application>Exchange</application> server has configured it, you can access "
"<application>Exchange</application> through IMAP as well. If you have got an "
"IMAP account, a user name and password, that is all you should need to use "
"&trojita; to access it."
msgstr ""
"Prvo trebate IMAP račun. Postoji mnogo provajdera;<ulink url=\"http://"
"fastmail.fm\">FastMail</ulink> je jedan;<ulink url=\"http://tuffmail.com"
"\">Tuffmail</ulink>  i  <ulink url=\"http://pobox.com\">Pobox</ulink> su "
"ostali. Google-ov Gmail usluga pruža pristup IMAP u vaš Gmail račun "
"(Outlook, a drugi ne).I ako menadžer vašeg &Microsoft; "
"<application>Exchange</application> server ga konfiguriše , možete "
"pristupiti <application>Exchange</application> putem IMAP. Ako ste dobili "
"IMAP račun, korisničko ime i lozinku, to je sve što vam treba da bi "
"koristili &trojita;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that not all IMAP providers are equal and some offer service that is "
"frustratingly slow. &Microsoft;'s <application>Exchange</application> server "
"too is reported to be somewhat slow. If you choose a good provider and use "
"fast software, you'll be surprised how pleasant an experience it can be."
msgstr ""
"Imajte na umu da nisu svi IMAP provajderi ravnopravni i neke ponude uslugu "
"su frustrirajuće spore. &Microsoft;'s <application>Exchange</application> i "
"server  prijavljen da je pomalo spor. Ako odaberete dobar provajder i "
"koriste brz softver, vi ćete biti iznenađeni kako ugodno iskustvo može biti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring your IMAP Account"
msgstr "Konfiguracija IMAP računa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, click on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab of the Settings box. "
"Add your IMAP account as a new account, using these parameters:"
msgstr ""
"Prvo , kliknuti na  <guilabel>General</guilabel> karticu postavki.Dodajte "
"vaš IMAP račun kao novi račun, koristeći ove parametre:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Real Name: the name you want to show on your emails (your own first and last "
"name)"
msgstr ""
"Pravo ime: ime koje želite da bude prikazano na vašem emailu(vaše vlastito "
"ime i prezime)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email: your email address"
msgstr "Email: Vaša email adresa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organisation: your company name (optional)"
msgstr "Organizacija: Ime Vaše kopanije(opcionalno)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Signature: any text you want to appear at the bottom of your emails, like "
"your website name or a slogan"
msgstr ""
"Potpis: bilo koji tekst koji želite da se pojavi na dnu Vašeg email-a, kao "
"što je website naziv ili slogan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These settings become an identity, and you can have several, if you want, if "
"for example, some of your mail is part of a mailing list where your messages "
"should look different (a different signature line, for example). Note "
"however that at present, &trojita; does not yet permit multiple IMAP "
"accounts (that is, use with multiple servers)."
msgstr ""
"Ove postavke postaju identitet, a možete ih imati više, ako želite, ako na "
"primjer, neki od vaših mailova je dio mailing listu gdje vaše poruke treba "
"da izgleda drugačije (drugačiji potpis, na primjer). Imajte na umu, međutim, "
"da u ovom trenutku, &trojita; još uvijek ne dopušta više IMAP računa (koji "
"je, uz korištenje više servera)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next, add the connection parameters necessary to access your account."
msgstr "Slijedeće, dodaj parametre veze neophodne za pristup vašem račun."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Method: choose SSL, if your provider requires it. Otherwise, choose \"TCP\" "
"for a connection that starts unencrypted and may be upgraded to encryption "
"while connecting. And if your provider requires you to perform that upgrade "
"to encryption, check the \"perform STARTTLS command\" to ensure it does. "
"\"Local process\" is for advanced users who, for example, are connecting to "
"their provider over another SSH agent (in this case you'd put something like "
"<userinput>ssh imap.provider.org dovecot --exec-mail imap</userinput>). "
"Generally, TCP or SSL are your two most likely choices."
msgstr ""
"Metoda: odaberite SSL, ako vaš provajder to zahtjeva. Inače, odaberite \"TCP"
"\" za vezu koja počinje nešifrovanu i može se nadograditi na enkripciju dok "
"se vrše povezivanja. A ako vaš provajder zahtijeva da izvrši nadogradnju na "
"enkripciju, provjerite \"obavljaju STARTTLS naredbu\" kako bi se osiguralo "
"to radi. \"Lokalni proces\" je za napredne korisnike koji, na primjer, se "
"povezujete svoje usluga u odnosu na drugu SSH agent (u ovom slučaju vi bi "
"stavili nešto poput <userinput>ssh imap.provider.org dovecot --exec-mail "
"imap</userinput>). Generalno, TCP ili SSL su vam dvije najvjerojatnije "
"mogućnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "IMAP Server: is your provider's server (&eg; mail.host.com)"
msgstr "IMAP Server: je server Vašeg provajdera (&eg; mail.domaćin.com)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Port: this parameter should change automatically depending on what you enter "
"for \"IMAP Server.\" Typically it is 143 for unencrypted connections and 993 "
"for SSL connections."
msgstr ""
"Port: ovaj parametar treba automatski promijeniti ovisno o tome što ste "
"unijeli za \"IMAP Server.\" Tipično je za 143 nešifrovanu veze i 993 za SSL "
"veze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Username: your username"
msgstr "Korisničko ime: Vaše korisničko ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Password: your password. At present, &trojita; stores your user name and "
"password in a plain text file on your computer. This is not secure! If that "
"worries you, leave the password field blank, and &trojita; will ask you once "
"for your password, and keep it in memory until the application exits."
msgstr ""
"Lozinka: Vaša lozinka. U ovom trenutku, &trojita; skladišti svoje korisničko "
"ime i lozinku u običnu tekstualnu datoteku na vašem računaru. Ovo nije "
"sigurno! Ako vas to brine, ostavite polje za lozinku prazno, i &trojita; će "
"vas pitati jednom za vašu lozinku, i čuvati je u memoriji dok se aplikacija "
"postoji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start in Offline Mode:"
msgstr "Početak u Offline Modu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Blacklisted Capabilities: &trojita; strives to be standards compliant. But "
"some servers that advertise standards compliance are not actually so. If "
"you're aware of some features that your provider advertises but does not "
"actually provide, listing them here allows &trojita; to politely ignore them."
msgstr ""
"Mogućnosti na crnoj listi: &trojita; nastoji da bude u skladu standardima. "
"Ali neki serveri koji reklamiraju sklad standarda nisu zapravo takvi. Ako "
"ste svjesni neke funkcije koju provajder reklamira, ali ih zapravo ne "
"obezbjeđuje, izlistavanje ovdje dopušta &trojita; da ih izignoriše."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Offline</guilabel> mode tab is where you configure &trojita;'s "
"ability to store local copies of messages on your server. The advantage of "
"saving a copy locally is obvious: you can access it later without "
"reconnecting. The disadvantages include filling up your local hard disk, and "
"of course the security risk if anyone ever goes exploring on your computer. "
"&trojita;'s default is to store local copies indefinitely, but here you may "
"choose if you prefer to store up to a certain number of days, or to not "
"store at all. Note that the code to clean the message cache has not yet been "
"implemented, so at present you should assume the message cache will not be "
"pruned."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Offline</guilabel> kartica za mod je gdje možete konfigurisati "
"&trojita; mogućnost čuvanja lokalne kopije poruka na serveru. Prednost "
"spašavanja kopije lokalno je očigledan: možete joj kasnije pristupiti bez "
"ponovnog konektovanja. Nedostaci uključuju punjenje hard diska, i naravno "
"sigurnosni rizik ako neko nekad bude istraživao nvaš računar. &trojita; će "
"zadano čuvati vašu poruku, ali možete odabrati ako vam je draže da pohraniti "
"do određenog broj dana, ili ne skladištiti nikako. Napomena da čišćenje keša "
"poruke nije još implementirano, tako da u ovom trenutku vam poruka ne bi "
"trebala biti odstranjeno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>SMTP</guilabel> tab is where you configure sending email."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>SMTP</guilabel> karitca je mjesto gdje možete konfigurisati vaše "
"emailove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Method: choose SMTP for unencrypted connections, or \"secure SMTP\" if you "
"prefer (and your provider accepts) mail sent over SSL. If you choose \"local "
"sendmail-compatible\" &trojita; will simply pass your mail to the sendmail "
"app running on your local computer (and if you haven't got one, it will "
"fail). Choosing this option requires you specify the sendmail parameters for "
"using your local sendmail."
msgstr ""
"Metoda: odabrati SMPT za nešifrovanu vezu, ili \"sigurni SMPT\" ako "
"preferirate (i vaš rovajder prihvati) poštu poslanu preko SSL. Ako odaberete "
"\"lokalno slanje pošte kompaktibilno\" &trojita; će jednostavno proslijediti "
"vašu poštu aplikaciji za slanje pošte koja je pokrenuta na vašem lokalnom "
"računaru (i ako ga ne budete imali, to neće uspjeti). Odabirom ove opcije "
"potrebno je specificirati  parametre slanja pošte za korištenje lokalnog "
"slanja pošte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "SMTP server: the name of the server to which your mail should be sent."
msgstr "SMPT server: ime servera kojem vaša pošta treba biti poslana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Port: This parameter should change automatically depending on what you "
"choose for \"Method.\" Typically, it's 587 for unencrypted mail, and 465 for "
"mail sent over SSL."
msgstr ""
"Port: Ovaj parametar promjene bi trebao automatski ovisno o tome što ste "
"izabrali za \"Metod\". tipično, to je za 587 nešifrovanu poštu, a 465 za "
"email poslat preko SSL."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sendmail Executable: is only required if you've chosen \"local sendmail-"
"compatible\" as your method. If so, here you should put whatever command is "
"required for your message to be sent to your local sendmail app. The default "
"is \"sendmail -bm -oi\" but if your local configuration is non-standard, "
"you'll have to adjust this parameter appropriately."
msgstr ""
"Šalji poštu izvršni: je potreban samo ako ste odabrali \"lokalni sendmail-"
"kompatibilne\" kao vašu metodu. Ako je tako, ovdje možete postaviti sve što "
"je potrebno za komandu vaše poruke poslati na svom lokalnom sendmail "
"programu. Standardno je \"sendmail -oi -bm\" cilj ako konfiguraciji vašeg "
"lokalnog je non-standard, podesit ćete ovaj parametar na-ima na odgovarajući "
"način."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"StartTLS: check this box if your provider requires a TLS connection to send "
"encrypted mail (this is not the same as using SSL by choosing \"Secure SMTP"
"\" as your method above)."
msgstr ""
"StartTLS: označite sljedeću kućicu ako vaš provider zahtijeva TLS vezu za "
"slanje šifrirane e-pošte (ovo nije isto što je korištenje SSL odabirom "
"\"Secure SMTP\" kao svoju metodu gore)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"SMTP Auth: if you must input a user name and password in order to send mail, "
"check this box. In the modern age, you almost always have to do so, as "
"otherwise spammers send unwanted messages through the server."
msgstr ""
"SMTP Auth: ako morate da unesete korisničko ime i lozinku kako bi poslao e-"
"mail, označite sljedeću kućicu. U moderno doba, skoro uvijek orate to "
"uraditi, u suprotnom spameri će poslati poruke putem servera."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Username: your user name."
msgstr "Korisničko ime: vaše korisničko ime."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your password."
msgstr "Vaša lozinka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save outgoing mail: if you check this box, &trojita; will save a copy of "
"every mail you send. This has been the default setting for all email "
"programs for so long now that few people even know it's possible to not do "
"so!"
msgstr ""
"Snimi odlaznu poruku: ako označite sljedeću kućicu, &trojita; će spasiti "
"kopiju svakog  e-maila koji šaljete. Ovo je bila zadana postavka za sve "
"programe e-pošte tako dugo sada kada malo ljudi zna za to i moguće da ne "
"učine!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sent folder name: If you do decide to keep a local copy of your sent mail, "
"choose in which folder you'd like to keep it."
msgstr ""
"Ime poslanog foldera: Ako odlučite da zadržite lokalnu kopiju poslanog "
"maila , birate folder u kojem ga želite zadržati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send with BURL: The BURL extension is an extension to the IMAP standard, "
"implemented in 2006, so not all servers make the service available. Imagine "
"you have a huge email in your inbox with an attachment, and you'd like to "
"forward that message. The normal way requires your IMAP client to download "
"that huge message, and then resend it (causing two large network transfers). "
"The BURL extension allows you to send that message without having to "
"download it first. If your provider permits BURL, it's worth selecting this "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Pošalji sa BURL: Produženje BURL je proširenje standardnog IMAP, Realizirana "
"2006. godine, tako da nisu svi serveri učinili dostupnim ovu uslugu. "
"Zamislite da imate veliku-pošte u vašem inboxu sa prilogom, a vi bih da "
"proslijedi poruku. Normalan način zahtijeva svoj IMAP klijent preuzimanje te "
"ogromne poruke i tada ga pošalje (Izazivanje dvije široke transferne mreže). "
"U BURL proširenje vam omogućuje slanje poruke bez da se to prvo preuzmete. "
"Ako vaš provider dopušta BURL, vredi Izborom ove opcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reading Mail with &trojita;"
msgstr "Čitanje emaila sa &trojita;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&trojita; presents a three paned interface that should be anyone who has "
"ever used email before. On the left side is a list of all your email "
"folders, probably INBOX and some others. On the right side are two panes: "
"the top pane shows the list of all messages in the current folder, and the "
"bottom pane shows the message selected in the top pane. &Microsoft; Outlook, "
"&kmail; and many other email clients all use this same layout."
msgstr ""
"&trojita; predstavlja tri sučelja koji bi trebao biti ako je iko ikada "
"koristili e-mail ranije. Na lijevoj strani je popis svih vaših e-mail mapa, "
"vjerovatno INBOX i neke druge. Na desnoj strani su dva okna: gornji panel "
"prikazuje popis svih poruka u trenutnom folderu, a donji panel prikazuje "
"poruke izabrani u gornjem panelu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other layouts are available, however. Under the <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"menu, simply select <menuchoice><guimenu>Layout</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Wide</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to choose instead a three pane layout suitable for "
"larger, wider screens, where your folders are shown in the left column, the "
"messages of the selected folder in the center column, and the contents of "
"the selected message in the right column."
msgstr ""
"Ostali rasporede su dostupni, kakogod. Pod <guimenu>View</guimenu> meniju, "
"jednostavno selektujte <menuchoice><guimenu>Layout</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Wide</guimenuitem></menuchoice> umjesto da izabere layout tri "
"panela pogodna za veće, 'šire ekrane na kojima su prikazani svi folderi u "
"lijevoj koloni, poruke o odabranoj mapi u centru koloni, i sadržaj odabrane "
"poruke u desnoj koloni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select a message, it will be displayed below. Right click on the "
"selected message in the top pane if you'd like to delete the message, save "
"it to disk as a text file, or view all the headers."
msgstr ""
"Kada odaberete poruka će se prikazati ispod njega. Desni klik na izabrane "
"poruke u gornjem panelu ako želite izbrisati poruke, spremiti na disk kao "
"tekstualnu datoteku, ili vidjeli sva zaglavlja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To respond to, or forward a message, use the buttons on the toolbar, as no "
"keystroke shortcuts are currently defined. Choose <guibutton>Private Reply</"
"guibutton> to respond only to the sender. Choose <guibutton>Reply to All</"
"guibutton> if you'd like to reply to the sender and everyone else on the To: "
"or CC: lines. If the message arrived through a properly-configured mailing "
"list, the <guibutton>Reply to Mailing List</guibutton> option will also be "
"made available."
msgstr ""
"Da biste odgovorili, ili proslijedili poruku koristite tipke na alatnoj "
"traci, kao ni na tastaturi prečica Ares trenutno definisana. Odaberite "
"<guibutton>Privatni Odgovori</guibutton>  da odgovarate samo pošiljaocu. "
"Odaberite <guibutton> Odgovori Svima</guibutton> ako želite odgovoriti "
"pošiljaocu i svi ostalima na Za: ili CC: linije. Ako je poruka stigla kroz "
"adekvatno konfigurirane mailing liste, <guibutton> Odgovori na mailing listu "
"</guibutton> opcija će biti stavljena na raspolaganje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "At present, the \"Forward message\" function has not yet been included."
msgstr "U ovom trenutku, funkcija \"Proslijedi poruku\" još nije uključena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing/Composing Mail"
msgstr "Pisanje/Sastavljanje pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To compose a new message, click the icon at the far left of the toolbar. A "
"new message window will appear, where you can choose your recipients, "
"compose your text, and send. If you get interrupted and need to save a "
"draft, you can do so by clicking on the little expander menu next to the "
"send button. A draft will then be saved in your drafts folder."
msgstr ""
"Da sastavite novu poruku, kliknite na zadnju lijevu ikonu alatne trake. "
"Prozor za novu poruku će se pojaviti, gdje odabitere primaoce, sastavljate "
"vaš tekst, i šaljete. Ako prekinete i trebate spasiti nacrt, to možete "
"učiniti klikom na mali izbornik pored dugmeta za slanje. Nacrt će biti "
"sačuvan u folder za nacrte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Address Book"
msgstr "Adresar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At present, &trojita; does not have a graphical addressbook, though one is "
"actively being developed. However, in the meantime, there's a very effective "
"work-around. Upon start up, &trojita; reads the address book located in "
"<filename role=\"directory\">~/.abook/</filename>, which you can create "
"using the console-only program called <application>abook</application>. "
"Running <application>abook</application> in a terminal window like "
"&konsole;, you can add, delete, and edit address book entries. &trojita; "
"doesn't manipulate that address book in any way, so for example, it won't "
"add new entries as you write messages. But if you've got an <filename role="
"\"extension\">.abook</filename> address book, &trojita; will auto-complete "
"entries using it."
msgstr ""
"U ovom trenutku, &trojita; nema grafičkog adresara, iako se jedan aktivno "
"razvija. Međutim, u međuvremenu, tu je vrlo efikasan rad-okolo. Nakon "
"pokretanja &trojita; čita adresar koji se nalazi na <filename role="
"\"directory\">~/.abook/</filename>, koje možete kreirati pomoću konzole-"
"jedini program pod nazivom  <application>abook</application>.Pokretanje  "
"<application>abook</application> u prozoru terminala kao u &konsole;, možete "
"dodavati,brisati i mijenjati unos adresara.&trojita;  ne manipulira "
"adresarom na bilo koji način, tako na primjer, neće dodavati nove stavke "
"kada pišete poruke. Ali kada dobijete <filename role=\"extension\">.abook</"
"filename> adresar,  &trojita; će koristeći ga automatski završiti unos."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Upute za naredbe"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &trojita; window"
msgstr "Glavni  &trojita; prozor"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "The IMAP Menu"
msgstr "IMAP meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compose Mail...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sastavi poštu...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new message for editing"
msgstr "Otvara novu poruku za izmjenu"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Expunge Mailbox</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Brisati Sadržaj Poštanskog "
"Sandučića</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes from the server any message already marked for deletion in the "
"currently selected mailbox (folder)."
msgstr ""
"Uklanja sa servera bilo koju poruku već označena za brisanje u trenutno "
"odabranom poštu folderu poštanskog sandučića."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Network Access</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Offline</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pristup Mreži</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Offline</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, &trojita; will not fetch any new data (messages) from your "
"server and will rather limit itself to the messages you have previously "
"downloaded. (It will still let you compose new messages, however, even "
"though you won't be able to send them)."
msgstr ""
"Ako je odabrano,&trojita; neće dohvatiti nikakve nove podatke (poruke) od "
"poslužitelja i već će se ograničiti na poruke koje ste prethodno skinuli. "
"(To će i dalje vam sastaviti nove poruke, međutim, iako nećete biti u "
"mogućnosti da ih pošaljete)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Network Access</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Expensive Connection</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pristup Mreži</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skupo Povezivanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this if you're using &trojita; on a cell-phone or other device where "
"it's important to reduce network traffic and be efficient."
msgstr ""
"Koristite ovo ako koristite &trojita; na mobilnom telefon ili drugom uređaj "
"gdje je to važno smanjiti mrežni promet i biti efikasan."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Network Access</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Free Access</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pristup Mreži</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Besplatan Pristup</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this if you are on a desktop computer with unlimited broadband internet "
"access. This permits &trojita; to more aggressively preload data. That is, "
"instead of just downloading headers, for example, it will go right ahead and "
"download a local copy of the messages, too."
msgstr ""
"Koristite ovo ako ste na desktop računaru s neograničenim širokopojasnim "
"pristupom internetu. Ovo dozvoljava &trojita; da agresivnije puni podatake. "
"To je, umjesto samo preuzimanje zaglavlja, na primjer, to će samo naprijed i "
"preuzeti lokalnu kopiju poruke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Layout</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Raspored</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guimenuitem>Wide</guimenuitem> for a modern, three-panel view with "
"the message list in the center and the message itself on the right. Choose "
"<guimenuitem>Compact</guimenuitem> for the traditional three panel view with "
"the message list on top and the message itself on the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Odabrati <guimenuitem>Širok</guimenuitem> za moderan, tro panelni pogled sa "
"listom poruka u centru i same poruke na desnoj strani."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Messages in Threads</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikazuje Poruke u Temama</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to show messages grouped into threads (conversations). "
"This is useful for mailing lists, for example. This depends on your IMAP "
"server supporting one or more voluntary extensions, as &trojita; would "
"otherwise have to do more work to properly thread messages."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite ovu opciju za prikaz poruke grupirane u teme (razgovore). Ovo je "
"korisno za mailing liste, na primjer. To ovisi o vašem IMAP server "
"podržavaju jedan ili više dobrovoljnih ekstenzija, kao &trojita; bi se inače "
"morala učiniti više posla da pravilno grupiše poruke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hide Read Messages</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sakriti Prošitane Poruke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose this option if you like only new messages to appear in the message "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite ovu opciju ako želite samo nove poruke da se pojave na listi "
"poruka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Only Subscribed Folders</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži samo Upisani Folders</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your mailbox may have more folders than you actually need to monitor. Select "
"this option to limit the folders shown to only those you've subscribed to. "
"(This doesn't delete the other folders, it just prevents them from being "
"shown in the list of folders)."
msgstr ""
"Vaš poštanski sandučić može imati više nego što zapravo monitor treba "
"pratiti. Izaberite ovu opciju da ograniči foldere pokazali samo one koje ste "
"pretplaćeni. (Ovo ne briše druge mape, samo ih sprečava da se prikazuje na "
"listi foldera)."

